    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Samartju nahze/ un winſch faz-\\\nzija us teem: Raugi/ zaar ta\\\nKUNGGA juhfo Tehwo Deewa\\\nBahrsibu pahr Juhdu/irr winſch\\\ntohs juhsfu Rohkâ dewis. Un\\\njuhs effat tohs nokawutchi ar\\\ntahdu Bahrsibu/ kas lihds Deb-\\\nbesim ſneeds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
